g.title: In this Lecture, Mr Robert C.Y.Wu would talk about Eslite Bookstore, his concept of reading, his thought of illnesses and wealth, and his view of peace, love and beauty of life.

In 1989, Mr Wu founded Eslite Bookstore, which he centered on a concept that encompassed the humanities, the arts, creativity and life. Through a uniquely creative operation model, which included the opening of a 24 hr bookstore.
